==English==

===Etymology===
The adjective is from {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|liberal|lang=fro}}, from {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|liberalis||befitting a freeman|lang=la}}, from {{term|liber||free}}; it is attested since the 14th century. The noun is first attested in the 1800s.

